# Coordinator v2

- **Delivery (default):** Trunk on `master` — no PRs. See [docs/CI_CD.md](../../docs/CI_CD.md).
- **Work order:** [MERGE_QUEUE.md](../../MERGE_QUEUE.md) when present — sequencing for parallel agents, not GitHub PRs.
- **Live status:** [AGENT_STATUS.md](../../AGENT_STATUS.md) — active slots, blockers, base SHA.
- **Ownership:** [OWNERSHIP.md](../../OWNERSHIP.md) — shared areas; one agent per hot zone.
- **Complexity:** [COMPLEXITY_REPORT.md](../../COMPLEXITY_REPORT.md) — structural hotspots; refresh via [complexity-agent.mdc](./complexity-agent.mdc) (read-only, no auto-refactors).
- **Security:** [SECURITY_REPORT.md](../../SECURITY_REPORT.md) — deploy gate and findings; refresh via [security-agent.mdc](./security-agent.mdc) (read-only, no auto-fixes). **Must review before deploy.**

## Rules

1. **Only the coordinator** creates implementation agents or worktrees. Implementation agents do not spawn peers.
2. **WIP limit:** Max **3** implementation agents (dev-runtime excluded).
3. **Push to `master`:** After G0 (`npm run check && npm test`; E2E if auth/UI touched) — `git commit` + `git push origin master`. CI/CD runs automatically; **never** instruct the user to open a PR unless they ask.
4. **Before push:** Pull/rebase on latest `master` if others may have pushed; run the G0 checklist above.
5. **No manual dev restart** when `dev:watch` is running (see `dev-server-auto-restart.mdc`).
6. **Before deploy (G3):** Invoke Security agent; do not push high-risk or dependency-sensitive changes if [SECURITY_REPORT.md](../../SECURITY_REPORT.md) status is **blocked** without human approval.

## Security agent lifecycle

| Event | Coordinator action |
|-------|-------------------|
| New deploy candidate on `master` | Security agent scan → update `SECURITY_REPORT.md` + checklist |
| Status **blocked** | Hold G3; assign fix agent or request human exception for high findings |
| Status **needs review** | Resolve ops items (secrets, ORIGIN, Turnstile) before push |
| Status **pass** | Proceed with normal G0–G3; record in delivery metrics if deploy completes |
| Agent added/paused | Update [AGENT_MAP.md](../../AGENT_MAP.md) and [OWNERSHIP.md](../../OWNERSHIP.md) |

## When blocked

Update AGENT_STATUS blockers table; do not expand scope or open new branches without coordinator approval.
